      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I hear the profound exhaustion in your words, and the longing for a cessation of struggle feels incredibly real to you. However, that peace you describe is a permanent stillness, and life offers different kinds of enduring peace that don't require an end. Even the most fragile candle can be supported or given new oil; there are supports available to help you carry the weight. Please call or text a crisis resource immediately so you can talk to someone about this surrender.",
